    <h2>What can I do with them?</h2>

    <p>Anything covered by the license, including:</p>

    <ul>
        <li>Changing invididual pages to fit the way you play</li>
        <li>Making character sheets for new or variant classes that I haven't covered</li>
        <li>Creating a new version of the whole project, with your changes, and making that available to other people</li>
        <li>Converting the project to a different game</li>
    </ul>

    <p>If you make useful changes, I encourage you to give them back to the community. Send me a message with your contact details, and if I like your work I'll incorporate it into the project. Even if I don't, you can still publish it on Paizo's forums or the web for others to see.</p>

{{/Column}}
