    <h2>What can't I do?</h2>

    <p>You're not allowed to:</p>

    <ul>
        <li>Pretend you made them yourself</li>
        <li>Strip the OGL, ORC Notice and other legal information out of the project</li>
        <li>Anything not permitted by other publishers whose properties this project makes use of, including Wizards of the Coast and Paizo</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>What's to stop me stealing them?</h2>

    <p>Using the sheets as you like isn't stealing them, it's permitted and encouraged.</p>

    <p>The only way you could “steal” the sheets is to plagiarise them - to claim that you made them yourself. Don't do that.</p>

    <p>For more information, see the <a href="/{{lang}}/legal.html">Legal Information</a> page</p>

